gw.api.iso

Class ISOCodeList

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.iso.ISOCodeList

  • public class ISOCodeList
extends java.lang.Object
    Code lists used in ISO requests. The request must contain a list of all the code lists it uses. This is just an enumeration of the code lists we know we will use. The actual CodeList XML records are generated automatically by examining the completed XML for all "codelistref" attributes and adding the appropriate CodeList records.
